com.epimorphics.jsonrdf.extras
Class JSStreamingWriter

java.lang.Object
  com.epimorphics.jsonrdf.extras.JSStreamingWriter

public class JSStreamingWriter
extends Object

A low level streaming JSON writer - assumes correct sequence of calls (e.g. keys in objects). Useful when writing JSON directly from some other structure.

Derived from JsonWriter to allow initialisation with a Writer and direct output of literals. This version checks that array and object brackets match and that only a single value appears at top level.
